# Monorepo Project Overview

This is a monorepo built with Turborepo containing multiple applications and shared packages.

## Structure

- [apps/](mdc:apps) - Contains all applications
  - [apps/token/](mdc:apps/token) - Main token/blockchain application
  - [apps/web/](mdc:apps/web) - Marketing website
  - [apps/docs/](mdc:apps/docs) - Documentation site
  - [apps/test/](mdc:apps/test) - Testing application

- [packages/](mdc:packages) - Contains shared packages
  - [packages/ui/](mdc:packages/ui) - Shared UI components
  - [packages/typescript-config/](mdc:packages/typescript-config) - Shared TypeScript configuration
  - [packages/tailwind-config/](mdc:packages/tailwind-config) - Shared Tailwind CSS configuration
  - [packages/transactional/](mdc:packages/transactional) - Transactional email templates

## Configuration Files

- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Root package.json with workspaces configuration
- [turbo.json](mdc:turbo.json) - Turborepo configuration
- [pnpm-workspace.yaml](mdc:pnpm-workspace.yaml) - PNPM workspace configuration
